title: Kopp's Frozen Custard with Marisa Pinson (LIVE)
itunes:title: Kopp's Frozen Custard with Marisa Pinson (LIVE)
description:
Marisa Pinson (Angie Tribeca, Don't Trust The B-) joins the 'boys to discuss Mitch's stomach ache and The Fonz before a review of Kopp's Frozen Custard. Plus, another edition of Drank or Stank. Recorded live at Turner Hall Ballroom in Milwaukee 8/5/22.
